<ul><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/Beloved" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/Beloved">Beloved</a></em>: Wei Wei tries to cover up the fact she's involved with a teenager by saying that she's her aunt.
</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/ElGoonishShive" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/ElGoonishShive">El Goonish Shive</a></em>: Ellen is Elliot's magically created <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OppositeSexClone" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OppositeSexClone">Opposite-Sex Clone</a>. She adopted the cover identity of being Elliot's twin sister, who had been in foster care most of her life.
